thread.title: Ashlee Lund

author: Ashlee Lund
title: Ashlee Lund
text: While I thought the shipping was a bit expensive, I will be ordering from screenprinting.com again! I can't wait to get my t-shirts in and begin using the high-quality product that I ordered to help learn more about producing high-quality prodcuts! One thing I would change are the assembly instructions as I don't know what certain parts of the product are called since I'm new to the screen printing business.
